 y74f ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">though it took all he had. </div><div class="t m5e3 xbc h30 y1ce7 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m35f x4b h30 y1ce7 ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Treasure Hidden. </div><div class="t m1a0 xe5 h4 y1ce7 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The treasure is </div><div class="t m19ce x20 h4 y14db ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">hidden, but not in the sense that God </div><div class="t me9 x20 h4 y1362 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">would keep it from us. It is hidden to those </div><div class="t m9d9 x20 h4 y13e6 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">only who have not yet found it. All who </div><div class="t m33e x20 h4 y1521 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">earnestly search will find it. </div><div class="t mad2 xbc h30 y111c ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m62a x4b h30 y111c ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Salvation an Individual Matter. </div><div class="t m453 x1a3 h4 y111c ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">There </div><div class="t m2134 x20 h4 y114d ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">is no gain in merely hearing about the </div><div class="t m6c2 x20 h4 yeb3 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">treasure. We must possess it for ourselves. </div><div class="t ma3b x58 h4 y1060 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">See John 4:39-42. </div><div class="t mad2 xbc h30 y14cf ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t ma70 x4b h30 yffd ff6 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Worthlessness of Earthly Treasure. </div><div class="t m200 x20 h4 ya21 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The worthlessness of material things is re-</div><div class="t mce5 x58 h4 y13b4 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">vealed by the rich fool. He overlooked the </div><div class="t mf4 x20 h4 y1444 ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">most important lesson of life, our obliga-</div><div class="t m586 x20 h4 y146b ff4 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">tion to God and to the needy. </div><div class="t m9cd x7d hb y14ff ff2 fs8 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">[ 13 ] </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
